node.title: Missing 10-year-old girl found safe and well
node.description: A 10-year-old girl who was missing in Dunedin has been found safe and well this morning.
node.content:
["A 10-year-old girl who was missing in Dunedin has been found safe and well this morning.", "", "
\nPhoto: 123rf\n
", "Police said earlier that the girl was last seen at her South Dunedin home at around 5pm yesterday.", "They said they had significant concerns for her safety.", "Their latest update said the girl had been found and police wanted to thank those who helped locate her."]
